commit.message:
feat(templates): canada theme plugin;

- Moved templates and helpers and public files/assets to a new plugin.
- Fixed page template.

fix(templates): error;

- Syntax.
- Remove debug stuff.

fix(templates): home;

- Syntax.
- Remove home index, template redirects do not work in flask.

fix(templates): admin config;

- Removed template.
- Always 404 view.

fix(templates): syntax;

- Cleaned up HTML for all templates.
- Removed some comments.

feat(templates): cdts;

- Finalized Portal and Registry menus.
- Added new error page templating.

removal(templates) misc;

- Removed unnecessary block.
- Removed unused template file.

fix(templates): misc translation handling;

- Fixed up some language conditions.
- Removed unused menu template.

fix(i18n): french colons;

- Put colons inside of gettext.
- Update PO files.

feat(css): datatables colvis popup;

- Finalized CSS.
- Added change log file.

